data.name: LBL_ABOUT_SUMMARY.Text
data.value: TS Finish is a powerful MPEG-TS packet processing tool. It modifies the MPEG-2 transport stream without changing the original packet payload. It adds, modifies and extracts MPEG-TS packets according to user needs. User may use TS Finish to rebuild PAT, PMT and SDT tables, or to change specific PID values. User can also discard or intercept data packets from the stream. TS Finish gives user the convenience of editing the underlying data of MPEG-TS.
